{"tid":2492792,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港青經墨西哥邊偷渡美國尋自由 助友被送移民監獄終獲批政庇","createTime":"2021-04-17T11:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T11:42:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1f799f4cc07a0a1bac47bdd3912aad741f73cff4","tid":2492792,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:30:43.000Z","msg":"19歲港青「錘佬」（化名），前年積極投入反送中運動，因擔心遭秋後算賬，決定逃離香港，獨自先到英國，再取道墨西哥偷渡入境美國，尋求政治庇護。周三（14日），「錘佬」終獲加州聖地牙哥移民法庭批出政治庇護，正式成為美國合法居民，這距離他今年1月從墨西哥邊境逃進美國剛超過3個月，距離正式開展政庇申請程序僅兩個月。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210417/5PSSR5QMBRAPNJ45EFLTCFDSU4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210417%2F5PSSR5QMBRAPNJ45EFLTCFDSU4%2F&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL79ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=8f0aecdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210417%2F5PSSR5QMBRAPNJ45EFLTCFDSU4%2F&h=4593059d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210417/5PSSR5QMBRAPNJ45EFLTCFDSU4/</a>"},{"pid":"d0cf80159c5418587e763d8889081476a2f1f30f","tid":2492792,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f799f4cc07a0a1bac47bdd3912aad741f73cff4","tid":2492792,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:30:43.000Z","msg":"19歲港青「錘佬」（化名），前年積極投入反送中運動，因擔心遭秋後算賬，決定逃離香港，獨自先到英國，再取道墨西哥偷渡入境美國，尋求政治庇護。周三（14日），「錘佬」終獲加州聖地牙哥移民法庭批出政治庇護，正式成為美國合法居民，這距離他今年1月從墨西哥邊境逃進美國剛超過3個月，距離正式開展政庇申請程序僅兩個月。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210417/5PSSR5QMBRAPNJ45EFLTCFDSU4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210417%2F5PSSR5QMBRAPNJ45EFLTCFDSU4%2F&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL79ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=8f0aecdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210417%2F5PSSR5QMBRAPNJ45EFLTCFDSU4%2F&h=4593059d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210417/5PSSR5QMBRAPNJ45EFLT